14 Jan 1683, bt, Maarup sogn, Johanne Stephensdatter d.o. Stephen Svendsen & Johanne Olufsdatter, fadd. Yde Olufsen - Niels Svendsen - Mads Thomsen - Maren Olufsdatter - Karen Jacobsdatter
13 May 1683, bt, Maarup sogn, Anders Stephensen s.o. Stephen Andersen & Zidsel Matthisdatter, fadd. Jens Laursen - Johanne Matthisdatter - Lars Juel - Zidsel Svendsdatter
29 Sep 1683, bt, Maarup sogn, Thoer Thomassen s.o. Thomas Thordsen & Mette Andersdatter, fadd. Peder Laursen - Lars Juel - Mette Jensdatter - Johanne Olufsdatter - Mette Ydesdatter
2 Sep 1683, bt, Maarup sogn, Jens Jensen s.o. Jens Laursen & Maren Jensdatter, fadd. Thomas Madsen - Stephen Andersen - Mette Jensdatter - Zidsel Matthisdatter
11 Nov 1683, bt, Maarup sogn, Helle Madsdatter d.o. Mads Mortensen & Margrethe Andersdatter, fadd. Mads Thomsen - ung Christen Juel - Zidsel Matthisdatter - Mette Pedersdatter
2 Feb 1684, bt, Maarup sogn, Maren Madsdatter d.o. Mads Thomsen & Maren Ydesdatter, fadd. Thomas Madsen - Yde Olufsen - Maren Olufsdatter - Margrethe Andersdatter
9 Jul 1684, bt, Vidstrup, Kirsten Larsdatter d.o. Lars Nielsen & Anne Nielsdatter, fadd. Peder Nielsen - Jens Nielsen - Anne Jensdatter Hjort - Margrethe Nielsdatter - Mette Ydesdatter
21 Sep 1684, bt, Vidstrup, Maren Andersdatter d.o. Anders i Vidstrup & Karen Jørgensdatter, fadd. Anders Matthisen - Peder Jørgensen - Kirsten Laursdatter - Johanne Pedersdatter - Maren Jensdatter
11 Jan 1685, bt, Maarup sogn, Maren Christensdatter d.o. Christen Juel & Maren Nielsdatter, fadd. Thomas Pedersen - Jens Laursen - Johanne Olufsdatter - Mette Pedersdatter
18 Mar 1685, bt, Maarup sogn, Zidsel Christensdatter d.o. Christen Juel & Zidsel Svendsdatter, fadd. Svend Laursen - Lars Juel - Christen Juel - Birgitte Nielsdatter - Margrethe Andersdatter

